T1  - The Case for the Natural Science Model For Research in Organizational Behavior And Organization Theory
AU  - Behling, Orlando
Y1  - 1980/10/01
PY  - 1980
DA  - 1980/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1980.4288944
