N2  - The concept of strategy continues to elude a common definition and operationalization. My purpose in this paper is to discuss alternative ways of operationalizing strategy, their strengths and limitations, and their appropriateness to different research questions. My particular focus is on business-level strategies, and I include an overview of available research questions involving business-level strategy.
